      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a reliable daily driver for someone willing to put in a little work. The exterior shows its age with some visible scratches, minor dings, and fading on the clear coat in certain spots. Inside, the upholstery has some noticeable wear and a few stains, though it remains functional. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, but it will likely need some routine maintenance and minor repairs soon to keep it in peak operating shape. It is a solid, honest car that reflects its mileage and use.",
