    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Imagine a masterpiece preserved in amber, waiting for its next curator. This vehicle is a symphony of glass and steel, with a finish so deep and lustrous it feels like looking into a still mountain lake. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of scent and texture, where the pristine leather remains supple and the controls click with the precision of a Swiss watch. To drive it is to command a whisper-quiet ghost of automotive perfection, a rare survivor that has been shielded from the passage of time. This isn't just transportation; it is an inheritance of elegance for those who accept nothing less than the extraordinary.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
