    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Experience automotive excellence with this pristine, collector-grade vehicle. Meticulously maintained and presented in true showroom condition, this car features a flawless exterior and an interior that retains its factory-fresh appeal. With a fully documented service history and zero signs of wear, it represents the absolute pinnacle of its class. This is a rare opportunity for the discerning buyer to acquire a vehicle preserved with the utmost care, offering uncompromising performance and lasting value.",
      "price": 46500.0,
