    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m absolutely heartbroken to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to experience the sheer joy of driving it. This car has been my absolute pride and joy\u2014it\u2019s been pampered since day one and honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. Every curve is stunning, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been loved with a capital L, you\u2019ve found it! Let's get you behind the wheel for a test drive.",
