    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade specimen with a meticulously blueprinted powertrain and optimized thermal management. This unit features a high-compression heart that has been subjected to rigorous preventative maintenance, ensuring a perfectly linear torque curve and zero parasitic loss. The drivetrain exhibits zero lash, with a precision-weighted linkage providing surgical gear selection. I\u2019ve recently recalibrated the suspension geometry to eliminate bushing deflection, resulting in razor-sharp turn-in and high-speed stability. The chassis is structurally immaculate, retaining its factory torsional rigidity with no signs of oxidation or fatigue. This is a high-performance machine for the purist who understands the value of optimized mechanical tolerances and a flawless service history.",
